name: Inconsistent laws
text:
§490:10-103.1  Inconsistent laws.  If any other provision of law is inconsistent with this chapter, this chapter shall govern unless this chapter or such inconsistent provision of law specifically provides otherwise. [L 1965, c 208, §10-103.1; HRS §490:10-103.1]
 
Case Notes
 
  Mentioned:  74 H. 1, 837 P.2d 1273.
